{"tid":594983,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[LOL]現在的LZ頗像當年的SKT(SKT無緣OFF SEASON有感)","createTime":"2018-03-16T09:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T14:40:56.000Z","uid":100551,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d47cd3ea2355dbb824f2835e19582687bcbf7d8","tid":594983,"uid":100551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"KHAN有多少FAKER那種你GANK他最後還是能跑掉的操作<br />\n雖然未完全到當年FAKER那樣2打1還是能殺你一個才跑掉<br />\n但現時要做到這點比當年難度大<br />\n當然KHAN遠沒有FAKER的沉穩<br />\n<br />\n然後2隊對地圖的經營也很全面<br />\n即使人頭無法領先很多~但是在搶目標物方面還能能比對手快一步<br />\n從而領先經濟(哪怕只有0.5-1K)<br />\n<br />\n線上的壓制力超強<br />\n以往的FAKER打線打爆之外還很強的支援<br />\n下路大多數時間都壓着對面打的~而且打得很穩<br />\n<br />\nJG是最不同的<br />\n但也無法說那一隊更好<br />\n<br />\nBP上不是現在的LZ有多好...<br />\n只是SKT的教練腦退化...<br />\n不知在想甚麼...看上場打BBQ真看不明...<br />\n<br />\n看着有些唏噓...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14744a944c43bb4a1f5a86533d6d83d1f5c7bc5c","tid":594983,"uid":84975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"faker老了"},{"pid":"8bf2a5ba1bf0c3d77a3407c113df561be37a8055","tid":594983,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:06:27.000Z","msg":"我睇咁耐比賽未試過見一隊野係毫無感情，毫無MISTAKE咁打機。 完全搵唔到突破位，你叫人點嬴？"},{"pid":"18a7f63b0be6133bc74c56f34217d1582bef9a2e","tid":594983,"uid":14082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bf2a5ba1bf0c3d77a3407c113df561be37a8055","tid":594983,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:06:27.000Z","msg":"我睇咁耐比賽未試過見一隊野係毫無感情，毫無MISTAKE咁打機。 完全搵唔到突破位，你叫人點嬴？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"咁熟既句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b54138a92d22c09546ef80e5ac9efac496b48f","tid":594983,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18a7f63b0be6133bc74c56f34217d1582bef9a2e","tid":594983,"uid":14082,"like":0,"d